29static INLINE int64_t
30timebase_units_to_ticks(const vpx_rational64_t *timestamp_ratio, int64_t n) {
31 return n * timestamp_ratio->num / timestamp_ratio->den;
32}
33
34static INLINE int64_t
35ticks_to_timebase_units(const vpx_rational64_t *timestamp_ratio, int64_t n) {
36 int64_t round = timestamp_ratio->num / 2;
37 if (round > 0) --round;
38 return (n * timestamp_ratio->den + round) / timestamp_ratio->num;
39}

41void vp9_set_first_pass_stats(VP9EncoderConfig *oxcf,
